--- !u!114 &4607188962686237356
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 5332158989428224651}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: fbeb6d65be27d3b40a131a1e4ace56b5, type: 3}
  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  steps:
  - message: The aircraft's spinning out of control already!
    character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: a80ac0751277f424ca977c804190eff8, type: 2}
    dontUseTTS: 0
    useAnimation: 0
    startTime: 0
    endTime: 0
    dialogueCondition: {fileID: 0}
  - message: "Steady, {player}. What you\u2019re seeing is rotation\u2014the aircraft
      turning around its own axis."
    character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 6a96359884e70134880e3323cd90c5eb, type: 2}
    dontUseTTS: 0
    useAnimation: 0
    startTime: 0
    endTime: 0
    dialogueCondition: {fileID: 0}
  - message: What exactly is rotation Gizmo?
    character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: a80ac0751277f424ca977c804190eff8, type: 2}
    dontUseTTS: 0
    useAnimation: 0
    startTime: 0
    endTime: 0
    dialogueCondition: {fileID: 0}
  - message: Rotation is the spinning movement of an object without actually leaving
      its position. kind of like how our planet has night and day.
    character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 6a96359884e70134880e3323cd90c5eb, type: 2}
    dontUseTTS: 0
    useAnimation: 1
    startTime: 0
    endTime: 1
    dialogueCondition: {fileID: 0}
  - message: What about revolution?
    character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: a80ac0751277f424ca977c804190eff8, type: 2}
    dontUseTTS: 0
    useAnimation: 1
    startTime: 1
    endTime: 2
    dialogueCondition: {fileID: 0}
  - message: Revolution is the movement of an object around the axis. It means object
      is said to be revolving if it is moving around a point or axis.
    character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 6a96359884e70134880e3323cd90c5eb, type: 2}
    dontUseTTS: 0
    useAnimation: 1
    startTime: 3
    endTime: 4
    dialogueCondition: {fileID: 0}
  - message: Got it. So this spinning is rotation, not revolution.
    character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: a80ac0751277f424ca977c804190eff8, type: 2}
    dontUseTTS: 0
    useAnimation: 1
    startTime: 4
    endTime: 5
    dialogueCondition: {fileID: 0}
  - message: "To describe that spin, we use angular position (\u03B8)."
    character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 6a96359884e70134880e3323cd90c5eb, type: 2}
    dontUseTTS: 0
    useAnimation: 0
    startTime: 0
    endTime: 0
    dialogueCondition: {fileID: 0}
  - message: "What is angular position (\u03B8) Gizmo?."
    character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: a80ac0751277f424ca977c804190eff8, type: 2}
    dontUseTTS: 0
    useAnimation: 0
    startTime: 0
    endTime: 0
    dialogueCondition: {fileID: 0}
  - message: "It denotes the orientation of a rotating object in free space. Unit
      is in radians (rads). One full rotation is 360\xB0 in degrees or 2\u03C0 rads
      in radians."
    character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 6a96359884e70134880e3323cd90c5eb, type: 2}
    dontUseTTS: 0
    useAnimation: 1
    startTime: 6
    endTime: 7
    dialogueCondition: {fileID: 0}
  - message: I understand now Gizmo! And how do we know how much the angle changes
      while it spins?
    character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: a80ac0751277f424ca977c804190eff8, type: 2}
    dontUseTTS: 0
    useAnimation: 1
    startTime: 7
    endTime: 8
    dialogueCondition: {fileID: 0}
  - message: "That\u2019s angular displacement (\u0394\u03B8). It is the measurement
      where the angle through which point, line or body has rotated in a specified
      direction, about a specified axis."
    character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 6a96359884e70134880e3323cd90c5eb, type: 2}
    dontUseTTS: 0
    useAnimation: 1
    startTime: 9
    endTime: 10
    dialogueCondition: {fileID: 0}
  - message: So it tells how far the aircraft rotated.
    character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: a80ac0751277f424ca977c804190eff8, type: 2}
    dontUseTTS: 0
    useAnimation: 1
    startTime: 10
    endTime: 11
    dialogueCondition: {fileID: 0}
  - message: "Correct! Then we have angular velocity (\u03C9)"
    character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 6a96359884e70134880e3323cd90c5eb, type: 2}
    dontUseTTS: 0
    useAnimation: 0
    startTime: 0
    endTime: 0
    dialogueCondition: {fileID: 0}
  - message: "What is angular velocity (\u03C9) Gizmo?"
    character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: a80ac0751277f424ca977c804190eff8, type: 2}
    dontUseTTS: 0
    useAnimation: 0
    startTime: 0
    endTime: 0
    dialogueCondition: {fileID: 0}
  - message: The rate of change in object's angular displacement over time. Just
      like the linear velocity, angular velocity also shows the rate of change in
      an object's position
    character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 6a96359884e70134880e3323cd90c5eb, type: 2}
    dontUseTTS: 0
    useAnimation: 1
    startTime: 12
    endTime: 13
    dialogueCondition: {fileID: 0}
  - message: So faster spinning means greater angular velocity.
    character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: a80ac0751277f424ca977c804190eff8, type: 2}
    dontUseTTS: 0
    useAnimation: 1
    startTime: 13
    endTime: 14
    dialogueCondition: {fileID: 0}
  - message: "Exactly. And when the spin speeds up or slows down, that\u2019s angular
      acceleration"
    character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 6a96359884e70134880e3323cd90c5eb, type: 2}
    dontUseTTS: 0
    useAnimation: 0
    startTime: 0
    endTime: 0
    dialogueCondition: {fileID: 0}
  - message: Tell me about angular acceleration Gizmo.
    character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: a80ac0751277f424ca977c804190eff8, type: 2}
    dontUseTTS: 0
    useAnimation: 0
    startTime: 0
    endTime: 0
    dialogueCondition: {fileID: 0}
  - message: It shows the changes in an object's angular velocity per unit time.
    character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 6a96359884e70134880e3323cd90c5eb, type: 2}
    dontUseTTS: 0
    useAnimation: 1
    startTime: 15
    endTime: 16
    dialogueCondition: {fileID: 0}
  - message: "Thanks for the information, Gizmo. I\u2019ll prepare for the quiz now!"
    character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: a80ac0751277f424ca977c804190eff8, type: 2}
    dontUseTTS: 0
    useAnimation: 1
    startTime: 16
    endTime: 17
    dialogueCondition: {fileID: 0}
